data.description: 2 homes on 20-acres that's nestled at the end of Cayley Way a private easement and only 6 minutes from Twin Oaks.  This little ranch has paid Solar that makes your monthly utility cost minimal, animal pens for your horses or kids 4-H projects. The main house was built in 2005 and is a 3 bedroom 2 bath that's 1456sqft home with a large covered front porch, corner fireplace, tile & wood floors, walk in master closet, and soaking tub in the master bath. The orginal Caretakers/Guest Home built 1986 is a 2 bed 1 bath at 624 square feet, complete with a wood burning stove.  This smaller home is perched beside the large steel building.  The property is fully fenced with multiple pasture areas, The corrals, shoots, and multiple pasture areas are set up as a turnkey Ranch Resort for your animals.  If you're looking for a Ranch with Privacy and all the fixings, including full solar, don't miss out on this one a kind find, priced to sell, move in ready.
